• lookup join (semi)
│ table: parent@primary
│ equality cols are key
│ lookup condition: (p_id = c_p_id) AND (crdb_region = 'ap-southeast-2')
│ remote lookup condition: (p_id = c_p_id) AND (crdb_region IN ('ca-central-1', 'us-east-1'))
